        <mxCell id="v_1504" parent="1" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Microsoft YaHei,Arial;fontSize=14;fontColor=#0B2A78;" value="&lt;b&gt;Mel-Spectrogram 输入经过 Encoder 提取连续潜在声学特征 z；随后将 z 分组，并对每组分别进行方向与模长离散化；最后将离散声学特征输入 Decoder，重建声学输出。&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:13px&quot;&gt;The encoder extracts continuous latent acoustic features z. The latent vector is divided into groups, and each group is quantized separately by direction and magnitude codebooks.&lt;br&gt;The merged quantized acoustic codes are then fed into the decoder to reconstruct acoustic output.&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="80" width="1430" x="295" y="942" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
